title: Level I Literacy Rates, Florida, 2004
name: Level I Literacy Rates, Florida, 2004
description: This dataset contains Level 1 Literacy Rates for Florida Cities and Towns with adult populations of at least 5,000. Literacy level 1 is the lowest literacy level. Adults in this category can perform simple tasks with text and documents, but display difficulty using certain reading, writing, and computational skills considered necessary for functioning in everyday life.
